,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"偷咩啫<br />\n中國人邏輯美國都係英國德國人黎血濃於水<br />\n但美國點解要益你中國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5a11efd420d510e80fef3bde67f1283df9c654","tid":1087201,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"都無撚理由偷埋和牛精液咁仆街掛"},{"pid":"a3e8a74a3e0bbbdf3eea8d3154c2c1164760dd61","tid":1087201,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"咪放長雙眼睇下美軍來了<br />\n國民帶唔帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}